main event: A balloon was sighted over Nellis AFB, Nevada on 9 Sep 55.
interesting points: The object appeared to be a balloon, possibly a 17 ft Meteorological Determination Indicator (MDI) balloon.
The object was seen stationary, but appeared to be moving slightly as it was obscured by clouds.
No other case files were found related to this sighting.
No photographs were taken of the object.
